This module references game mechanics and terminology from the D&D 5th Edition
Systems Reference Document (SRD 5.1), which is available under the Creative
Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC-BY-4.0) by Wizards of the
Coast. See: https://dnd.wizards.com/resources/systems-reference-document

This module does NOT distribute, reproduce, or bundle any copyrighted content
from Wizards of the Coast. SRD-licensed content (races, classes, spells,
monsters, etc.) is accessed at runtime from the user's own Foundry VTT dnd5e
system compendium packs — which are provided by the dnd5e system module under
its own license.

Non-SRD race names present in the source code are used solely as mechanical
lookup keys (speed, size, darkvision values) for validation purposes. Game
mechanics are not copyrightable. No descriptions, lore, or creative content
from non-SRD sources is distributed with this module.

AI-Generated Content Disclaimer

All NPCs, player characters, item descriptions, racial traits, and other
narrative content produced by this module are generated dynamically by
third-party AI services (OpenAI, Google, xAI, etc.) at the user's request
using the user's own API key. This AI-generated content is NOT created,
reviewed, or endorsed by the module author. The module author makes no
guarantees about the accuracy, balance, or appropriateness of AI-generated
content. All generated actors and items should be reviewed and adjusted by the
Game Master before use in play.
